creator: KnightOwl.xyz
descriptionHtml:
Stake is easy, fun, and free—Swipe Right to Like someone, Swipe Left to pass. If someone likes you back, It’s a Match! Swipe, match, and chat online with your matches, then step out and meet up in the real world and make something worth remembering.

Now, start swiping. And remember, Everyone deserves someone, we help you to find your perfect one

Welcome to Stake— World's first free dating app, no cost, just swipe

FEATURES?
Stake comes with features, including Unlimited Likes so you can Swipe Right to your heart’s content, Passport to chat with singles anywhere around the world, Unlimited Rewind to give someone a second chance.

MORE FEATURES?
We assure you, you never have to pay a single penny for any upcoming feature

Life is short, make it worth remembering.
